==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sonless
<hw>Son"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Being without a son.</def>
<rj><au>Marston.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>As no baron who was <qex>sonless</qex> could give a husband to his
daughter, save with his lord's consent.</q> <rj><qau>J. R.
Green.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sonnet</ent>⟦br⟧
